OL,6,FFormer Harry Potter actor Rupert Grint
OL,7,Fmust pay more than #1.8 million in tax
OL,8,Fafter losing a legal battle with HM
OL,9,FRevenue and Customs.
OL,11,FMr Grint, who played Ron Weasley in
OL,12,Fthe franchise, was ordered to pay the
OL,13,Fsum in 2019 after HMRC launched an
OL,14,Finvestigation into his tax return from
OL,15,Fthe 2011-12 tax year.
