OL,3,CRupert Grint ordered to pay further
OL,4,C#1.8m in tax
OL,6,FAt a hearing in the First-Tier
OL,7,FTribunal, held in London in November
OL,8,Fand December 2022, lawyers for Mr
OL,9,FGrint appealed against HMRC's
OL,10,Fdecision, arguing that the right
OL,11,Famount of tax had been paid.
OL,13,FBut in a ruling, Tribunal Judge
OL,14,FHarriet Morgan dismissed the appeal,
OL,15,Ffinding that the sum "is taxable as
OL,16,Fincome".
