OL,6,FShe said that the money "derived
OL,7,Fsubstantially the whole of its value
OL,8,Ffrom the activities of Mr Grint",
OL,9,Fwhich was "otherwise realised" as
OL,10,Fincome in the 2011/12 tax year.
OL,12,FMr Grint starred in the first Harry
OL,13,FPotter film in 2001 as a teenager and
OL,14,Fis calculated to have earned around
OL,15,F#24 million from playing Ron Weasley.
OL,17,FHe previously lost a separate court
OL,18,Fbattle concerning a #1 million tax
OL,19,Frefund in 2019.
